124
00:13:45,279 --> 00:13:48,149
SPEAKER_20: It's all in order, I'll be going.

125
00:13:49,919 --> 00:13:54,379
SPEAKER_20: Master Fugui, don't think badly of me...

126
00:13:54,860 --> 00:13:56,950
SPEAKER_20: for leaving you homeless.

127
00:13:57,960 --> 00:14:00,590
SPEAKER_20: But I sure like that mansion of yours.

128
00:14:00,899 --> 00:14:03,230
SPEAKER_20: See you there in a few days.

131
00:14:10,409 --> 00:14:12,710
SPEAKER_20: Master Fugui, I'm sorry...

132
00:14:12,779 --> 00:14:15,769
SPEAKER_20: but you've nothing left.
What would you wager?

186
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:49,500
SPEAKER_20: Your mother's not well.
Go now, for her sake.

228
00:24:09,470 --> 00:24:11,769
SPEAKER_20: This old home of yours is great.

229
00:24:12,180 --> 00:24:14,369
SPEAKER_20: Warm in winter, cool in summer.

230
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:16,470
SPEAKER_20: Great at any price.

231
00:24:19,420 --> 00:24:22,009
SPEAKER_20: I've given up the puppet troupe.

232
00:24:22,119 --> 00:24:23,519
SPEAKER_20: Have a seat.

233
00:24:25,619 --> 00:24:28,990
SPEAKER_20: I don't gamble anymore.
Don't want to end up like you.

242
00:25:10,829 --> 00:25:13,930
SPEAKER_20: I never had to beg
when I ran the puppet troupe.

243
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:16,190
SPEAKER_20: Earn your money yourself.

244
00:25:17,539 --> 00:25:19,529
SPEAKER_20: Put together a troupe.

780
01:28:19,590 --> 01:28:20,920
SPEAKER_20: I'll be going.

954
01:44:16,710 --> 01:44:18,039
SPEAKER_20: Chunsheng.

955
01:44:23,149 --> 01:44:24,779
SPEAKER_20: What do you want?

956
01:44:26,949 --> 01:44:28,850
SPEAKER_20: Come out for a second.

1085
01:53:49,579 --> 01:53:51,909
SPEAKER_20: I wouldn't dare.

